West_Des_Moines.Dale Maffitt Reservoir:
Maffitt Lake is a reservoir in the four corners of Dallas County, Polk County, Warren County, and Madison County, Iowa. It is located at 41.517°N 93.792°W﻿ / 41.517; -93.792.
It is owned by the Des Moines Water Works that serves as an emergency water supply for the city of Des Moines, Iowa.
